{"id": "1240126153029582878", "channel_id": "1240032956454801603", "type": 19, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "胚胎幾乎拿來生吃，唯羊媽每回合會吞一顆雙胞胎，\n這隊雖然也是鑰狂互充但與純混還是多了一些不同的優點，\n例如每回合保底20%全隊暴率、疊力量、精通盾、熔爐、可以自選對象的30狂氣", "timestamp": "2024-05-15T02:18:35.312000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1137328302135181312"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1240121766903283803", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1240032956454801603", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "羊媽雲攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1240126784326860830", "channel_id": "1240032956454801603", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "當然也可以帶血肉角，只是若沒有其他人協助產胎的話他自己就沒胎吞，\n畢竟羊媽自己造三吞三沒有多餘胎能產出", "timestamp": "2024-05-15T02:21:05.825000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1240032956454801603", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "羊媽雲攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179734373019748"]}
