{"id": "1240132240785018890", "channel_id": "1240032956454801603", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "我應該明確一點羊媽的優勢：\n付出成本：3費靈知覺醒、每回合2費\n●每回合穩定的觸發血肉精通\n●每回合提供隊友36狂氣\n●每回合開一次血與沙鑰令\n\n純混沒有24的話，要能夠有每回合都兩次鑰令精通也不太容易，\n有24的話就是當前版本T0這點羊媽比不過", "timestamp": "2024-05-15T02:42:46.746000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-15T03:18:55.462000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1240032956454801603", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "羊媽雲攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1240132686421557268", "channel_id": "1240032956454801603", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "羊媽拿來複製神父的應消確實不錯，\n但可能會中斷羊媽的狂氣循環，還是爆發回合在這麼做比較好\n複製受祝骨血有回胎比較能兼顧神父疊傷與羊媽的回狂", "timestamp": "2024-05-15T02:44:32.994000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-15T02:47:06.411000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1240032956454801603", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "羊媽雲攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179734373019748"]}
